'''妊娠線'''在[[懷孕|懷孕]]後三個月時，在腹部會出現的深色垂直線<ref name="pmid7832550">{{cite journal |author=Estève E, Saudeau L, Pierre F, Barruet K, Vaillant L, Lorette G |title=Physiological cutaneous signs in normal pregnancy: a study of 60 pregnant women |language=fr |journal=Ann Dermatol Venereol |volume=121 |issue=3 |pages= 227–231 |year=1994 |pmid=7832550 |doi= |url=}}</ref>。妊娠線為咖啡色，寬約一公分，一般會沿著[[腹部|腹部]]中線，從[[恥骨|恥骨]]延伸到[[肚臍|肚臍]]，不過有些也會延伸到肚臍的上方<ref>[http://pregnancyandb
aby.com/pregnancy/baby/Whats-my-line-All-about-the-linea-nigra-4210.htm She Knows Network: "What's that line? All about linea nigra"]{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。妊娠線是因為[[胎盤|胎盤]]產生的[[促黑素細胞激素|促黑素細胞激素]]增加而造成<ref name="Reproductive System at a Glance">{{cite book|last=Heffner|first=Linda|title=The Reproductive System at a Glance|url=https://archive.org/details/reproductivesyst03edheff|year=2010|publisher=Wiley-Blackwell|isbn=978-1-4051-9452-5|pages=[https://archive.org/details/reproductivesyst03edheff/page/51 51]}}</ref>，促黑素細胞激素也會造成[[黑斑|黑斑]]及[[乳頭|乳頭]]顏色變深。

皮膚白皙的女性比較不容易出現妊娠線，皮膚較黑的女性比較容易出現<ref>{{cite web|last1=Pregmed|first1=Editor|title=Linea nigra and pregnancy|url=http://www.pregmed.org/linea-nigra.htm|publisher=Pregmed|accessdate=22 February 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150222205751/http://www.pregmed.org/linea-nigra.htm|archive-date=2015-02-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。妊娠線一般會在分娩後幾個月後消失。

